snippet.title: EEK3 Indie Horror Showcase
snippet.description:
Join us to watch Skully present the EEK3 Indie Horror Showcase! Showing 40+ trailers for projects released or releasing this year.

You can submit theme suggestions for the summer game jam at http://summer.hauntedps1.com and you  can visit the virtual showfloor at http://showfloor.hauntedps1.com 

Thanks everyone who watched EEK3 live!

Video produced by Amos Sorri
